The Jamie Bartlett team discovered that half a million members are fans of far-right groups in Europe. It targeted them with announcements, but instead of linking them to a new group or product, the announcements invited users to respond to an investigation. The questions asked concerned their level of education, their attitudes to violence and their optimism about their own future.
