The Communications and Transport Secretariat (SCT) reported that the results highlighted the accident in which the Secretary of Government, Francisco Blake Mora and seven other persons lost their lives, indicate that the helicopter has hit the ground directly in complete structural integrity, without the pilot being able to try a forced landing.
